# Professional Agency UI Overhaul Plan

Elevate the Ark Engine website from a "tech-demo" aesthetic to a "Professional Agency" powerhouse. The goal is to balance futuristic innovation with corporate elegance, reliability, and visual depth.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This overhaul will introduce more structured layouts and a more sophisticated color palette (Deep Navy/Slate accents) to replace the high-contrast monochromatic look. I will also be reducing the size of the massive "9xl" headers for better professional hierarchy.

