## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- **Visual Audit**: Ensure the typography hierarchy feels balanced across all screen sizes.
- **Aesthetic Check**: Confirm the move to slate/navy accents creates more visual depth.
- **Image Integration**: Verify that new generated assets load correctly and match the brand theme.
